{"word":"Thankfulness","slug":"thankfulness","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Thankfulness</b> Jesus set an example of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=11&verse=25'>Mat 11:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=27'>Mat 26:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=11&verse=41'>Joh 11:41</a><br/> The heavenly host engage in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=4&verse=9'>Rev 4:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=7&verse=12'>Rev 7:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=11&verse=17'>Rev 11:17</a><br/> Commanded<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=50&verse=14'>Psa 50:14</a><br/> Should be offered:<br/> - To God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=50&verse=14'>Psa 50:14</a> <br/> - To Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=1&verse=12'>1Ti 1:12</a> <br/> - Through Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=1&verse=8'>Rom 1:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=3&verse=17'>Col 3:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=13&verse=15'>Heb 13:15</a> <br/> - In the name of Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=5&verse=20'>Eph 5:20</a> <br/> - In behalf of ministers<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=1&verse=11'>2Co 1:11</a> <br/> - In private worship<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=6&verse=10'>Dan 6:10</a> <br/> - In public worship<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=35&verse=18'>Psa 35:18</a> <br/> - In everything<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=5&verse=18'>1Th 5:18</a> <br/> - Upon the completion of great undertakings<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=31'>Neh 12:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=40'>Neh 12:40</a> <br/> - Before taking food<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=11'>Joh 6:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=27&verse=35'>Act 27:35</a> <br/> - Always<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=1&verse=16'>Eph 1:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=5&verse=20'>Eph 5:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=1&verse=2'>1Th 1:2</a> <br/> - As the remembrance of God's holiness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=30&verse=4'>Psa 30:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=97&verse=12'>Psa 97:12</a> <br/> - For the goodness and mercy of God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=106&verse=1'>Psa 106:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=107&verse=1'>Psa 107:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=136&verse=3'>Psa 136:3</a> <br/> - For the gift of Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=9&verse=15'>2Co 9:15</a> <br/> - For Christ's power and reign<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=11&verse=17'>Rev 11:17</a> <br/> - For the reception and effectual working of the word of God in others<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=2&verse=13'>1Th 2:13</a> <br/> - For deliverance through Christ, from indwelling sin<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=7&verse=25'>Rom 7:25</a> <br/> - For victory over death and the grave<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=15&verse=57'>1Co 15:57</a> <br/> - For wisdom and might<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=2&verse=23'>Dan 2:23</a> <br/> - For the triumph of the gospel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=2&verse=14'>2Co 2:14</a> <br/> - For the conversion of others<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=6&verse=17'>Rom 6:17</a> <br/> - For faith exhibited by others<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=1&verse=8'>Rom 1:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=53&chapter=1&verse=3'>2Th 1:3</a> <br/> - For love exhibited by others<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=53&chapter=1&verse=3'>2Th 1:3</a> <br/> - For the grace bestowed on others<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=1&verse=4'>1Co 1:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=1&verse=5'>Phi 1:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=1&verse=6'>Col 1:6</a> <br/> - For the zeal exhibited by others<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=8&verse=16'>2Co 8:16</a> <br/> - For nearness of God's presence<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=75&verse=1'>Psa 75:1</a> <br/> - For appointment to the ministry<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=1&verse=12'>1Ti 1:12</a> <br/> - For willingness to offer our property for God's service<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=29&verse=14'>1Ch 29:14</a> <br/> - For the supply of our bodily wants<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=14&verse=7'>Rom 14:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=4&verse=4'>1Ti 4:4</a> <br/> - For all men<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=2&verse=1'>1Ti 2:1</a> <br/> - For all things<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=9&verse=11'>2Co 9:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=5&verse=20'>Eph 5:20</a> <br/> Should be accompanied by intercession for others<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=2&verse=1'>1Ti 2:1</a>; <a href='